      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Purified monomeric actin was prepared from rabbit skeletal muscle by extraction from an acetone powder, a cycle of polymerization and depolymerization, and gel filtration on a 2.5 x 50 cm or a 1.5 x 40 cm column of Sephadex G-150 medium (equilibrated with buffer G consisting of 2 mM Tris-Cl, 0.5 mM dithiothreitol, 0.2 mM ATP, 0.2 mM CaC12) to remove actin oligomers and minor contaminating proteins."
